enb_long_title: SIXTH CONFERENCE OF THE PARTIES TO THE UN FRAMEWORK CONVENTION ON CLIMATE CHANGE RESUMED SESSION
section_title: IMPACT OF SINGLE PROJECTS ON EMISSIONS IN THE COMMITMENT PERIOD
sentences: Due to time constraints, this issue was not discussed in-depth during SBSTA.
Parties decided at the final COP plenary to refer the decision (FCCC/CP/2001/2/Add.5), as elaborated during COP-6 Part I, for adoption in its current format at COP-7.
